type: txt
syntax:expression: $VAR(@) in "no", "direct", "mst"; "Invalid value."
allowed: echo "no direct mst"
help: Mode for sending broadcast packets to other deamons
help_val: no; Broadcast packets are never sent to other nodes.
help_val: mst; Broadcast packets are sent and forwarded via the VPNs Minimum Spanning Tree.
help_val: direct; Broadcast packets are sent directly to all nodes that can be reached directly.
